high_descs: Walk forward to face the round table.
Pick up the sponge from the table next to the spoon.
Walk around the table to reach the round plate sitting on the table.
Set the sponge down on the round plate.
Pick up the round plate and sponge from the table.
Turn around to face the cabinets under the microwave.
Put the sponge and plate in the right cabinet underneath the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge on a plate from the table into the right cabinet under the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight and stop at the round table on the left
Grab a bar of soap off of the table
Turn left and go to the other side of the round table
Put the soap on the plate
Grab the plate off of the table
Turn right and face the cabinets on the bottom
Put the plate in the second cabinet from the bottom
anns.task_desc: Putting a plate with a bar of soap on it in a cabinet

high_descs: Go forward and turn left to face the table.
Pick up the sponge from the table.
Turn around completely and walk around the right side of the table. Turn left to face the table.
Place the sponge on the plate on the table.
Pick up the sponge and plate from the table.
Walk to the left and go to the counter across from the table
Open the cabinets under the counter and place the items inside.
anns.task_desc: Move a sponge and plate to the cabinets.
